column5: Much tougher walking conditions after the snowy week. Already some slush under the snow....fishing was tougher...not many marked...and very gentle bite. Tried different depth and eventually Meegs got me limit of whities plus a nice BBQ size laker. Lets see how ice will do in the next week or so and if there will be couple more ice trips. Few shots:        Cheers, Ice Fisherman
Well done Emil. Walking was tough. I think this weekend will be the last kick.  Nice catch bud.
